title: Helping Others Improve- EP 15

embed.description: This is part of a series, where I try and help others go from Bronze to silver. Heck maybe even gold. Im not the one playing, Im spectating a game. If you are bronze and want some help, let me know.

body:
If you guys have time, I'm starting to think it would be a good idea, to have discussions on the boards, on what could have been done better.

So to anyone who wants too, point out what I missed, so this guy can get better.
And also point out what I can do, to help them get better.
